snippet.title: PAC-MAN Tamagotchi by Bandai America
snippet.description:
PAC-MAN and Tamagotchi have collaborated to celebrate the 40th Anniversary of PAC-MAN! You can now raise and nurture your Tamagotchi character with the help of PAC-MAN. If the ghosts and bugs invade the screen, call PAC-MAN in to help before it’s too late! For even more fun, you can play the Pac Game and the Catch Game! There are two different versions of the PAC-MAN Tamagotchi, the yellow maze and the black maze, and comes with a chain so you can take your PAC-MAN Tamagotchi everywhere! Batteries (LR44) included.

Available March 15th, 2020 at Target, Amazon and GameStop!
